Blue Enamel Seahorse Stud Earrings - Complete Pair

combinations.description: A charming pair of blue enamel seahorse stud earrings outlined in gold-tone metal. These petite novelty studs feature a glossy ocean-blue finish with sculpted detailing and a raised metallic border that highlights the seahorse silhouette. Lightweight and whimsical, they are perfect for beachwear, summer outfits, nautical themes, or vintage jewelry collectors.
